description: Returns the number of unmetered iOS or unmetered Android devices that have been purchased by the account.

nested_items.name: awsAccountNumber
nested_items.description: The AWS account number specified in the AccountSettings container.

nested_items.name: unmeteredDevices
nested_items.description: Returns the unmetered devices you have purchased or want to purchase.

nested_items.name: unmeteredRemoteAccessDevices
nested_items.description: Returns the unmetered remote access devices you have purchased or want to purchase.

nested_items.name: maxJobTimeoutMinutes
nested_items.description: The maximum number of minutes a test run executes before it times out.

nested_items.name: trialMinutes
nested_items.description: Information about an AWS account's usage of free trial device minutes.

nested_items.name: total
nested_items.description: The total number of free trial minutes that the account started with.

nested_items.name: remaining
nested_items.description: The number of free trial minutes remaining in the account.

nested_items.name: defaultJobTimeoutMinutes
nested_items.description: The default number of minutes (at the account level) a test run executes before it times out. The default value is 150 minutes.

nested_items.name: skipAppResign
nested_items.description: When set to true, for private devices, Device Farm does not sign your app again. For public devices, Device Farm always signs your apps again.
